values:
I'm going to end this journal for two reasons:

1) It's too hard for me to sign out and sign back in again on this name
2) It is making people mad that there are somethings I would just rather not tell everyone. And some people don't understand that, hence the rift being caused

So now I say goodbye...and if there is anything deep that I would have put on here...I will go back to the old-fashioned ways of telling people myself.
